<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
  xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="launchpad"
>

<body>
  <div metal:fill-slot="body">
  <tal:block define="flavour_name view/flavour/title;
                     series_name view/series/title">
  
    <h1>Requesting an Ubuntu CD</h1>

    <p>Ubuntu is available free of charge and we can send you a CD of the
    latest version (<span tal:replace="series_name" />) with no extra
    cost, but the delivery may take up to ten weeks, so you should consider
    downloading the CD image if you have a fast Internet connection.
    </p>
    
    <table id="chooseLinks">
      <tr>
      <tal:no-prerelease condition="not: view/prerelease_mode">
        <td class="cdchoice" width="45%">
          <a href="login">Request a CD of Ubuntu Desktop Edition</a>
        </td>
        <td width="10%">&nbsp;</td>
        <td class="cdchoice" width="45%">
          <a href="login-server">Request a CD of Ubuntu Server Edition</a>
        </td>
      </tal:no-prerelease>
      <tal:prerelease condition="view/prerelease_mode">
        <td class="cdchoice" width="45%">
          <a href="login">Pre-order a CD of Ubuntu Desktop Edition</a>
        </td>
        <td width="10%">&nbsp;</td>
        <td class="cdchoice" width="45%">
          <a href="login-server">Pre-order a CD of Ubuntu Server Edition</a>
        </td>
      </tal:prerelease>
      </tr>
    </table>
  
    <p><a href="login">Check the status of an existing request</a></p>

  </tal:block>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
